articles.headline: Kraken sign forward John Hayden to 2-year contract extension
articles.description: Seattle signed forward John Hayden to a two-year, one-way contract extension Wednesday.

articles.headline: With Stars struggling to score, Oilers have a chance to wrap up West final in Game 5
articles.description: — The Dallas Stars are back home and on the verge of their season ending in the Western Conference final for the third year in a row — especially if they don't start scoring goals again like they did all season.

articles.headline: Jets captain Adam Lowry has hip surgery, out 5-6 months
articles.description: Jets captain Adam Lowry is expected to miss five to six months after having hip surgery, the team announced Wednesday.

images.name: Adam Lowry [1296x729]
images.caption: Keep reading to see why Adam Lowry of the Winnipeg Jets should be in your lineups this week.
images.alt: Adam Lowry #17 of the Winnipeg Jets hits the ice prior to puck drop against the Minnesota Wild at the Canada Life Centre.

images.name: Alex Petrovic's punishing hit flips Adam Lowry into the bench
images.caption: Alex Petrovic gets a hard hit on Adam Lowry that sends him into the Winnipeg bench.

articles.headline: 2025 Stanley Cup playoffs: Latest championship, Conn Smythe odds
articles.description: Every playoff team's odds to win the 2025 Stanley Cup and favorites for the Conn Smythe Trophy for playoff MVP.

images.name: Aleksander Barkov [1296x729]
images.caption: Which team will raise the Stanley Cup this season?

images.name: Mikko Rantanen [800x450]
images.caption: Mikko Rantanen of the Dallas Stars (R).

images.name: Frederik Andersen of Carolina Hurricanes [608x342]
images.caption: Canes goaltender Frederik Andersen delivered a shutout in Game 3 against the Capitals and is among the Conn Smythe favorites.

images.name: Subban: Oilers 'undisciplined' to allow Stars' comeback win
images.caption: P.K. Subban breaks down what went wrong for the Oilers in the third period when the Stars scored five straight goals.

articles.headline: Reigning Stanley Cup champion Panthers get second shot at closing out Hurricanes in Eastern final
articles.description: — The Florida Panthers missed on their first chance to eliminate the Carolina Hurricanes and return to the Stanley Cup Final for the third...

images.name: Canes snap 15-game ECF losing streak to stay alive
images.caption: The Hurricanes defeat the Panthers in Game 4 to get their first Eastern Conference finals win since 2006.

articles.headline: Mammoth sign 2023 first-rounders Dmitri Simashev, Daniil But
articles.description: The Utah Mammoth are bringing over two of their top prospects from Russia in time for next season, signing defenseman Dmitri Simashev and forward Daniil But to three-year entry-level contracts.
